Resource Profile: CH EPREG Patient: Mother

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epreg/StructureDefinition/ch-epreg-patient-mother Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2025-05-22 Computable Name: ChEpregPatientMother

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This profile constrains the Patient resource to represent the pregnant individual.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH EPREG Composition, CH EPREG Coverage, CH EPREG Encounter: Mother, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Abdominal Circumference... Show 9 more, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Blood Pressure, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Body Weight, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Fundus Height, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Gestational Age in Days, CH EPREG Observation (Base): Pregnancy Progress, CH EPREG Observation (Base): Results Laboratory, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Urine Finding, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Vagina Feature and CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Weight Gain
